rows.label: qev041602_MSG0001
rows.name: Oh-ho-hooo! Customer! Welcome, friend![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0002
rows.name:
...Muh? Friend not here to shop? Friend only here
looking for huge thing that stole cargo of Kuta?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0003
rows.name: Wanana saw it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0004
rows.name:
It came from the sky. It got dark all around so fast,
Wanana thought night came early.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0005
rows.name: Then huge thing came crashing down![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0006
rows.name:
It picked up cargo with wiggly-woobly arms and
legs and then swooped off![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0007
rows.name: Whole thing was over in seconds.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0008
rows.name:
Oh, and it flew off toward west. ...It felt kind of
south-y too, but it was definitely on left-hand side of
Wanana.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0009
rows.name:
Not sure what direction Wanana was facing at the
time, though.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0010
rows.name: But who care about details? Not Wanana![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0011
rows.name:
Still, Wanana hope friend can get cargo back soon.
Wanana will take big hit without it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0012
rows.name:
When new product is big hit, Wanana like that.
But when profits TAKE big hit? No sirree![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0013
rows.name: So Wanana has been thinking...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0014
rows.name:
What if huge thief thing was actually TINY thing
riding on huge vehicle?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0015
rows.name:
And what if tiny thing was master thief who already
sold off stolen cargo?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0016
rows.name:
Aaaugh! It would be too late!
Kuta never get it back![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0017
rows.name:
Hmm? Friend looks awfully satisfied.
Did something good happen?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0018
rows.name:
...What? Friend beat huge thief thing and got back
cargo of Kuta?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0019
rows.name:
Oh-ho-hoooo! After story like that, friend deserves title
of legendary warrior![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041602_MSG0020
rows.name: Now hurry and give that cargo to the boss.[ST:wait ]
